qStringExpression.qExpr: 'The number of purchased professional licenses for the current month.'

qDef.qDef:
Dual(
  'data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="12" width="' & Num(80+$(vProSVGPadPx)) & '">'
  &'<text text-anchor="end" font-family="Source Sans Pro" font-size="9" fill="black">'
  &'<tspan dominant-baseline="central" text-anchor="end" x="' & Num($(vProSVGPadPx)) & '" y="5.5">' 
  & Num([# Professional Assigned by Tenant (Current)],'#,##0') & '</tspan></text>'
  & '<rect x="' & Num(5+$(vProSVGPadPx)) & '" y="0" width="50" height="12" style="fill:%23F0F3F6" />'
  & '<rect x="' & Num(5+$(vProSVGPadPx)) & '" y="2" width="' & Round([% Professional Assigned by Tenant (CM)]*100/2,1) & '" height="8" style="fill:%23' & If(Num([% Professional Assigned by Tenant (CM)])<$(vProLowThresh),'$(vBelowLowThreshColor)',If(Num([% Professional Assigned by Tenant (CM)])<$(vProHighThresh),'$(vBelowHighThreshColor)','$(vAboveHighThreshColor)')) & '" />' 
  &'<text text-anchor="start" font-family="Source Sans Pro" font-size="9" fill="black">'
  &'<tspan dominant-baseline="central" text-anchor="middle" x="' & Num(68+$(vProSVGPadPx)) & '" y="5.5">' 
  & Num([% Professional Assigned by Tenant (CM)],'#,##0%') & '</tspan></text>'
  & '</svg>',
  Num([% Professional Assigned by Tenant (CM)])
)
